node.text: Join @ashleygraham and I as we discuss the NEW! @sttropeztan Self Tan Ultimate Glow Kit in collaboration with Ashley Graham. My absolute favorite self tanner I have tried so far. The full transformation at the end is EXACTLY why I love it. You can see the results so clearly and how much GLOW my skin has. What an incredible product. Who's tried it? Get it now at @ultabeauty #ashleygraham #sttropez #sttropeztan #sttropezpartner

node.text: As someone who has loved and supported @jaclynhill for over 8 years, I am so proud of her. Watching her growth and success has been so inspiring. You can genuinely see the love and dedication Jaclyn has put into her brand since she first launched it. With each set back, she has risen up and absolutely KILLED IT. Sell out after sell out. I truly believe no one deserves it more. This is what years of hard work looks like. This collection, along with her others, is STUNNING. S T U N N I N G. Not a single complaint. I am impressed beyond words with @jaclynhill and I honestly cannot wait to see what else is to come from @jaclynhillcosmetics. Major congrats on this collection! Definitely get your hands on it when it launches if you can, it is more than worth it.

node.title: Is the new @jaclynhillcosmetics Haute Topic summer collection worth it?

node.text:
This may the prettiest I have ever felt! 

Have you ever tried a full face of one brand? Today I went for @ctilburymakeup because they had gifted me a bunch of products to try! I was BEYOND excited about the result. 

What’s ONE brand that you would love to do a FULL face of? 😳

Here are the products I used in order:

- Magic Serum Crystal Elixir 
- Magic Cream
- Hollywood Flawless Filter (Shade 1 Fair)
- Airbrush Flawless Foundation (Shade 5 Neutral) (I am Shade 1 Neutral when not tanned)
- Magic Away Concealer (Shade 2 Fair) 
- Airbrush Flawless Finish Powder (Shade 1 Fair) 
- Hollywood Contour Wand (Shade Light to Medium)
- Hollywood Light Wand (Shade Pillow Talk, Used as Blush)
- Hollywood Light Wand (Shade Spotlight, Used as Highlighter)
- NEW! Brow Cheat (Shade Medium Brown) 
- NEW! Legendary Brows (Shade Dark Brown)
- Pillow Talk Luxury Palette
- Hollywood Flawless Eye Filter (Limited Edition) 
- Pillow Talk Push Up Lashes Mascara
- Lip Cheat Lip Liner (Shade Foxy Brown) 
- Hot Lips Lipstick (Shade Kim K.w.) 
- Airbrush Flawless Setting Spray

- Tag a friend in the comments!

node.text:
6 MILLION!!!!! I cannot BELIEVE it! I remember some said to me last year “I wonder if you’ll ever have 1 million followers” and I responded “no I don’t think that’ll ever happen I don’t fit the mold” and I sit here today just hitting 6 million followers. Wow. It’s truly unbelievable to me. I am so grateful for all of you. I have had so much fun the last year and a half and YOU have made this experience so special for me. I have grown so much as a person and you all also got to witness me fall madly in love and much more. If you’ve been here since the beginning, thank you for following my journey. And if you’re a newer follower, I’m so excited for you to see what’s to come. Thanks for being here. 

I have the biggest giveaway I’ve done coming soon and I am so thrilled. I love giving back to the people who make this possible for me. Let’s have some fun! Stay tuned.

node.text: As someone who has loved and supported @jaclynhill for over 8 years, I am so proud of her. Watching her growth and success has been so inspiring. You can genuinely see the love and dedication Jaclyn has put into her brand since she first launched it. With each set back, she has risen up and absolutely KILLED IT. Sell out after sell out. I truly believe no one deserves it more. This is what years of hard work looks like. This collection, along with her others, is STUNNING. S T U N N I N G. Not a single complaint. I am impressed beyond words with @jaclynhill and I honestly cannot wait to see what else is to come from @jaclynhillcosmetics. Major congrats on this collection! Definitely get your hands on it when it launches if you can, it is more than worth it.

I have never loved a look more. Recreation of @shyshbeauty Mikayla x @glamlite look. THE BEST COLOR is 🔥🔥🔥

Also wearing Code Orange lashes and MxGL nude gloss! 

Restock is available for pre order for the collection and palette on @glamlite and you can use code MIKAYLA 💚🤗

Want me to recreate your Mikayla x @glamlite look? Be sure to tag me in your posts and use the mikaylaxglamlite hashtag!
